

						
						     Tip of the Day   Don't be insensitive. Sometimes I have to catch myself on this one because men and women view many things in life with emotional differences. Girls can cry about the weirdest, most unimportant things. Guys can often not be emotional when its appropriate. Make sure that when your girl is upset, or happy, or worried, or scared that you aren't being an insensitive jackass and making stupid comments about it. 

						
